- 1 = 27/27
- 1/3 = 9/27
- 1/27 = 1/27

P(A₁ ∪ A₂ ∪ A₃) = 27/27 - 9/27 + 1/27 = (27 - 9 + 1)/27 = 19/27

Converting to decimal: 19/27 ≈ 0.7037

